title: YOU CAN BUY WITH DOWN PAYMENT ASSISTANCE PROGRAM $3000-$4000 DOWN!!!
posting_body: ['QUIT LOOKING AROUND & THE OPPORTUNITY IS HERE!!!', 'First time home buyer can purchase this house with as little as $3000-$4000 down!', 'If you are looking to upgrade your residency look no further.', 'If you are looking for a peace of mind of no rent increase, own this house with first time home buyer program.', 'There are many programs which allow you to buy with 1.0%-1.5% down, the government and the lender will assist you with 3% down & closing credit.', 'It is a great program to buy your first home which is as little as $3000-$4000 down.', 'I specialize in first time home buyer.', 'I will walk you through the entire process.', 'I will get you pre-approved and walking you into your dream home.', 'Ask about our down payment programs.', 'No one is better with more experience or expertise to help you.', 'CALL TODAY', 'show contact info', 'John Khaw', 'Service You Deserve.', 'Realtor You Trust', 'BRE 01947490', 'Direct', 'show contact info', 'Nationwide Real Estate Executives', '6850 Lincoln Ave Suite 200', 'Buena Park, Ca 90620', '{Specializing in Orange County, Los Angeles County, Riverside County, and San Bernardino County}', 'Picture shown is for illustration purpose only.', 'Actual home meets first time home buyer program.']
